<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="strict-adj">strict <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /strɪkt/    美 /strɪkt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>严格的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>School regulations were strict.
学校的规章制度很严格。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 2</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) strict with sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think teachers need to be strict with students.
我认为老师应该对学生严格要求。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) strict about sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be strict about work / discipline
对工作/纪律要求严格</p></div></div>